<header>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="column full">
        <div class="overlay animated fadeIn"></div>
        <article class="animated fadeIn">
          <h1 id="logo">Splashbox</h1>
          <p>Hi-resolution photos delivered to your Dropbox</p>
          <small id="version">Version 1.0</small>
          <a class="button" href="<%= auth_url %>"><button class="purple">Get Started &rarr;</button></a>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<section id="stats">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="column full">
        <h3 class="animated fadeInUpBig"><span class="photo-count count odometer" data-count="<%= @photo_count %>"></span> photos delivered to over <span class="user-count count odometer" data-count="<%= @user_count %>"></span> Dropbox accounts</h3>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="column half">
        <h2>Connect Your Dropbox.</h2>
        <p>You'll need to <a href="<%= auth_url %>">authorize</a> your Dropbox account with us and provide access for us to push new photos to your account when they become available.</p>
        <a class="button" href="<%= auth_url %>"><button class="purple">Connect Now &rarr;</button></a>
      </div>
      <div class="column half animated fadeIn">
        <%= image_tag 'dropbox.svg', width: '213', height: '225' %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="column half">
        <h2>Watch the Waitlist.</h2>
        <p>Due to current demand I've had to create a waitlist. Once you've connected your Dropbox account you'll be placed on the waitlist.</p>
        <p>Your spot on the waitlist can be seen in your dashboard.</p>
        <a class="button" href="<%= dashboard_path %>"><button class="purple">View Waitlist &rarr;</button></a>
      </div>
      <div class="column half animated fadeIn">
        <%= image_tag 'watch.svg', width: '295', height: '231' %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="column half">
        <h2>Get Photos.</h2>
        <p>Once your account is activated, you will start seeing photos being delivered to your Dropbox.</p>
        <p>Your initial payload will include <span class="payload-count count odometer" data-count="<%= @payload_count %>"></span> photos curated by the <a href="http://unsplash.com">Unsplash</a> team. Thereafter, every 10 days or so you will automatically receive another set of 10 photos delivered to your Dropbox.</p>
        <p>You just sit back and relax.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="column half animated fadeIn">
        <%= image_tag 'computer.svg', width: '295', height: '386' %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%= render 'footer' %>
